argument.name: TargetContainer
argument.description: The destination container where items are copied.

page.description: This function will copy all items that are newer to another SubContainer.
page.example:
dim SubContainer as A5Storage::SubContainer = null_value() dim TargetSubContainer as A5Storage::SubContainer = null_value()
CallResult = A5Storage::SubContainer::Open(SubContainer, "Provider='Disk';Container='c:\A5Webroot';", "logs") ?CallResult.Success = .T.
CallResult = A5Storage::SubContainer::Open(TargetSubContainer, "Provider='Disk';Container='c:\A5Webroot2';", "logs") ? CallResult.Success = .T.
? SubContainer.CopyNewContentsTo(TargetSubContainer) = .T.
